com.cyc.session

Interface CycSessionConfigurationProperties


  • public interface CycSessionConfigurationProperties
    This defines the canonical set of names for all CycSessionConfiguration properties. Although some implementations of the CycSessionConfiguration interface may not require these keys, they should be used in any implementation backed by Properties or any form of map with String-based keys.
